channel.title: Is FoundationIndustries still being developed?
channel.description: @HappyJamCoding, just dropping you a line to let you know I enjoyed using FoundationIndustries previously. I have recently picked Satisfactory up again after Update 4 and wondered if you were still supporting FoundationIndustries and if there might be a compatible version soon. Thanks for all your hard work, and I hope to see a new version!
